All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, ExtractExtension, LayerExtension
public class BaseExtractExtension
extends BaseLayerExtension
implements ExtractExtension

Implements a base Extract LayerExtension, that is used for layers involved in data downloading activities from an ArcIMS ExtractService.
